flowchart TD
    A[Open execution-report.json] --> B{dry_run}
    B -- true --> C[Expect skipped actions]
    B -- false --> D[Expect success or failed actions]
    C --> E[Check summary.skipped equals summary.total]
    D --> F[Check summary.failed]
    F -- 0 --> G[Check discovery counts and spot-check results]
    F -- "greater than 0" --> H[Filter failed results by action_id and error_type]
    H --> I[Trace action_id in plan.json]
    I --> J[Fix plan, plugin, or handler]
    G --> K[Promote run result]
